parameters:
Shop Owner: We have a selection that even the Magic Academy
recognizes.

Shop Owner: Please go to the desert town of Ammos and see
the merchant Oro. He's not an easy man to deal with...

events.name: 取り置きのクリスタル

parameters:
Shop Owner: Well, well, if it isn't Lady Relm. What kind of
merchandise are you looking for today?

Mage Relm: Today, I'm running an errand for Dokusa-san. I've
come to collect the reserved crystals.

Shop Owner: Crystals, huh... They were left untouched for
over half a year, so I ended up selling them.
Mage Relm: This is troublesome... May I ask who bought them?

Shop Owner: I am Oro, the traveling merchant for magicians.
I am currently in the desert city of Ammos.
Shop Owner: Um... Lady Relm, about this matter...

Mage Relm: It's okay, Dokusa-san is completely at fault, so
please rest assured.

Shop Owner: Without the trust of the Magic Academy, the
business in this town cannot thrive.
Shop Owner: Please continue to support us in the future.
